sequenceDiagram
    participant ESP as ESP32 Nodes
    participant Pi1 as Raspberry Pi 1<br/>(Primary)<br/>172.20.10.10
    participant Pi2 as Raspberry Pi 2<br/>(Backup)<br/>172.20.10.11
    
    Note over ESP,Pi1: Normal Operation
    ESP->>Pi1: Publish sensor data
    Pi1->>ESP: ACK
    Note over Pi1: Store in InfluxDB<br/>Display on Grafana
    
    Note over ESP,Pi2: Pi 1 Failure Detected
    ESP-xPi1: Connection attempt 1 (FAIL)
    ESP-xPi1: Connection attempt 2 (FAIL)
    ESP-xPi1: Connection attempt 3 (FAIL)
    
    Note over ESP: Automatic Failover<br/>Triggered
    ESP->>Pi2: Connect to backup broker
    Pi2->>ESP: ACK
    ESP->>Pi2: Publish sensor data
    Note over Pi2: Store in backup InfluxDB
    
    Note over ESP,Pi2: Background Primary Retry
    loop Every 60 seconds
        ESP->>Pi1: Check if primary available
        Pi1--xESP: Still unavailable
    end
    
    Note over ESP,Pi1: Pi 1 Recovers
    ESP->>Pi1: Primary check (SUCCESS!)
    Pi1->>ESP: ACK
    Note over ESP: Auto-reconnect to Primary
    ESP->>Pi1: Resume normal operation
    Note over Pi1: Back to primary database